1) How do I get more information about my new UPS shipping account?
If you opened a new UPS shipping account from the plug-in, a confirmation email with more information will be sent to the email address that you entered while creating the new account.
//======================= Par lapu:
1) Kā iegūt plašāku informāciju par savu jauno UPS piegādes kontu?
Ja atvērāt jaunu UPS piegādes kontu, izmantojot spraudni, uz e-pasta adresi, kuru ievadījāt, tiks nosūtīts apstiprinājuma e-pasts ar plašāku informāciju. izveidojot jaunu kontu.

//======================= About page:
2) How do I prepare my packages for UPS collection or drop off to a UPS Access Point™?
Refer to the package preparation recommendations at this link - https://www.ups.com/%1/%2/services/individual-shipper/preparing-to-ship.page
//======================= Par lapu:
2. Kā sagatavot pakas UPS savākšanai vai nodot uz UPS Access Point™ atrašanās vietu?
Skatiet iepakojuma sagatavošanas ieteikumus šajā saitē - https://www.ups.com/%1/%2/services/individual-shipper/preparing -to-ship.page

//======================= About page:
3) How do I give my packages to UPS?
You can drop you packages at any authorized UPS location such as a UPS Access Point™. Click below to search for a convenient access point location near you.
//======================= Par lapu:
3. Kā es varu nodot savas pakas UPS?
Jūs varat nodot savu paku jebkurā pilnvarotā UPS vietā, piemēram, UPS Access Point™ vietā. Noklikšķiniet tālāk, lai meklētu ērtu atrašanās vietu netālu no jums

//======================= About page: If you have UPS packages on most business days and would prefer a regular UPS pickup, you can email a completed and signed Pickup form to the following email address - konto@ups.com. //======================= About page: By installing UPS Plugin you gained this convenient option to apply UPS recommended Security Enhancements to your e-shop.By enabling particular security enhancements below you can make your e-shop less vulnerable to some common hackers' attacks.

Note, you can keep UPS recommended Security Enhancements disabled if you have already implemented these security measures in other way (by tweaking your web servers configurations properly, by coding own Magento hooks or by using some other plugin that aims to implement the similar enhancements).
//======================= Par lapu: Instalējot UPS spraudni, jūs ieguvāt šo ērto iespēju savā e-veikalā lietot UPS ieteiktos drošības uzlabojumus. Iespējojot noteiktus drošības uzlabojumus zemāk, jūs varat padarīt savu e-veikalu mazāk neaizsargātu pret dažiem izplatītiem hakeru uzbrukumiem.

//======================= About page: Note, you can keep UPS recommended Security Enhancements disabled if you have already implemented these security measures in other way (by tweaking your web servers configurations properly, by coding own Magento hooks or by using some other plugin that aims to implement the similar enhancements).

See [wikipedia|https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Clickjacking] for more details. If you enable this defense, then UPS plugin will secure your store by communicating framing policy to user's browser through 'X-Frame-Options: Sameorigin' HTTP response header and by injecting 'frame-breaker' java script for legacy browsers.- UPS Plugin can secure your e-shop Front Office pages in accordance with OWASP recommended Clickjacking Defense Cheat Sheet Disable this defense if you wish to enable framing of your e-shop GUI on 3rd party websites; or if you have already implemented this defense differently.
//======================= Par lapu: Plašāku informāciju skatiet vietnē [wikipedia|https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Clickjacking]. Ja iespējosit šo aizsardzību, UPS spraudnis nodrošinās jūsu veikala drošību, paziņojot lietotāja pārlūkprogrammai ietvaru politiku, izmantojot HTTP atbildes galveni X-Frame-Options: Sameorigin un ievadot mantotajām pārlūkprogrammām java skriptu "frame-breaker".- UPS spraudnis. var aizsargāt jūsu e-veikala Front Office lapas saskaņā ar OWASP ieteikto Clickjacking Defense Cheat Sheet Atspējojiet šo aizsardzību, ja vēlaties iespējot sava e-veikala GUI kadrēšanu trešo pušu vietnēs; vai ja jūs jau esat ieviesis šo aizsardzību savādāk.

//======================= About page:
See wikipedia for more details.If you check this option, UPS plugin will secure your e-shop Front Office by applying
X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
//======================= Par lapu:
Lai iegūtu sīkāku informāciju, skatiet Wikipedia. Ja atzīmēsit šo opciju, UPS spraudnis nodrošinās jūsu e-veikala Front Office, piemērojot
X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff

//======================= About page: HTTP Response Header to all Magento Front Office pages. That will prevent the client's browser (notably Internet Explorer) from MIME-sniffing a response away from the declared content-type. You may not really need this as your users are not supposed to upload any potentially harmful files to your e-shop (e.g. JavaScript instead of an Image). However, it is still good practice to enable this special security header as there is no performance penalty associated with it.
//======================= Par lapu: HTTP atbildes galvene visām Magento Front Office lapām. Tas neļaus klienta pārlūkprogrammai (īpaši Internet Explorer) MIME izsmelt atbildi no deklarētā satura veida. Jums tas var nebūt vajadzīgs, jo jūsu lietotājiem nav jāaugšupielādē jūsu e-veikalā iespējami kaitīgi faili (piemēram, JavaScript attēla vietā). Tomēr joprojām ir laba prakse iespējot šo īpašo drošības galveni, jo ar to nav saistīts darbības sods.

//======================= About page: Enables cross-site scripting filters in browsers that support the X-XSS-Protection directive
//======================= Par lapu: Iespējo starpvietņu skriptu filtrus pārlūkprogrammās, kas atbalsta direktīvu X-XSS-Protection

//======================= About page:
See wikipedia for more details.If you check this option, UPS plugin will secure your e-shop Front Office by applying
X-XSS-Protection: '1; mode=block'
HTTP response header to all Magento Front Office pages.
//======================= Par lapu:
Sīkāku informāciju skatiet wikipedia. Ja atzīmēsit šo opciju, UPS spraudnis nodrošinās jūsu e-veikala Front Office aizsardzību, izmantojot
X-XSS-Protection: '1; mode=block'
HTTP atbildes galvene visām Magento Front Office lapām.

//======================= About page: Protect your e-shop website against protocol downgrade attacks and cookie hijacking
//======================= Par lapu: Aizsargājiet savu e-veikala vietni pret protokolu pazemināšanas uzbrukumiem un sīkfailu nolaupīšanu

//======================= About page:
See wikipedia for more details If you check this option, UPS plugin will secure your e-shop Front Office by applying
Strict-Transport-Security 'max-age=31536000; includeSubDomains'
HTTP response header to all Magento Front Office pages.
//======================= Par lapu:
Plašāku informāciju skatiet wikipedia Ja atzīmēsiet šo opciju, UPS spraudnis nodrošinās jūsu e-veikala Front Office, piemērojot
Strict-Transport-Security 'max-age=31536000; includeSubDomains
HTTP atbildes galvene uz visām Magento Front Office lapām.

//======================= About page: Prevent sensitive pages from caching by browser.
//======================= Par lapu: Neļaujiet sensitīvām lapām saglabāt pārlūkprogrammas kešatmiņu.

//======================= About page:
See OWASP FAQs for more details. If you check this option, UPS plugin will secure the Checkout process by applying
Cache-Control: no-cache, no-store
Expires: 0
Pragma: no-cache
HTTP response headers to the corresponding pages
//======================= Par lapu:
Plašāku informāciju skatiet OWASP BUJ. Ja atzīmēsit šo opciju, UPS spraudnis nodrošinās Checkout procesu, piemērojot
Cache-Control: bez kešatmiņas, bez veikala
Derīguma termiņš: 0
Pragma: bez kešatmiņas
HTTP atbildes galvenes uz attiecīgajām lapām
